1. Kubernetes kya hai?

Container Orchestration tool — jab tumhare paas bahut saare Docker containers hain, unko manage, scale, aur deploy karne ke liye
Google ne banaya tha, ab Cloud Native Computing Foundation (CNCF) manage karta hai
K8s bhi kehte hain (K + 8 letters + s)


2. Kubernetes ke Benefits:

Auto-scaling — load badhe toh automatically containers badh jaayein
Self-healing — agar koi container crash ho, woh automatically restart ho jaye
Load balancing — traffic evenly distribute hoti hai containers ke beech
Rolling updates — bina downtime ke naya version deploy karo
Rollback — agar naya version fail ho, purana version wapas lao
